Your problem is on this line:

    if (p2==p1)

You&#39;re comparing the memory addresses to see if they are equal, but NOT the contents stored at (i.e. pointed to in) them. To compare the passwords, instead use:

    if (strcmp(p2, p1) == 0)

See: https://www.tutorialspoint.com/c_standard_library/c_function_strcmp.htm

